 inherit;\">Hướng dẫn chế biến:&nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Thịt bụng bò Úc thích hợp với các món xào, nhúng lẩu.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; min-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: inherit;\">-------------------</span></span></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0.5em 0px 0.2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; min-width: 100%; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: inherit;\">Vì sao nên chọn mua thịt nhập khẩu&nbsp;tại La Maison?</span></span></span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; min-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: inherit;\">-&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: inherit;\">La Maison&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">- Chất lượng hàng đầu</span>. Được n</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: inherit;\">hập khẩu từ các quốc gia có nền chăn nuôi tiên tiến và công nghệ chế biến thịt hàng đầu thế giới như Đan Mạch, Đức, Pháp, Tây Ban Nha, Mỹ, Canada, Úc, Argentina...</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; min-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">- Tươi ngon tự nhiên - An toàn sức khỏe</span>. Giống heo thịt, bò thịt danh tiếng thế giới, được</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: inherit;\">&nbsp;chăn nuôi hoàn toàn tự nhiên, cho thịt chất lượng cao và thơm ngon hảo hạng.</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; min-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">- Công nghệ bảo quản hiện đại</span>&nbsp;giúp duy trì, bảo toàn và hoàn nguyên chất lượng thịt, đảm bảo thịt sau khi hoàn nguyên vẫn tươi ngon tự nhiên.</span><br><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: inherit;\">-&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">Chất lượng dịch vụ chuyên nghiệp</span>, an toàn, tiện lợi và luôn hướng đến khách hàng.</span></span></p>', '0', '2020-08-18 10:56:09', '2020-08-18 11:26:13');
