e: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">Hướng dẫn bảo quản:</span>&nbsp;</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; min-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: inherit;\">Bảo quản ở nhiệt độ&nbsp;≤&nbsp;-18⁰C.&nbsp;Sử dụng trong thời hạn 7 ngày khi chuyển sang bảo quản ở nhiệt độ 0⁰C tới 4⁰C.&nbsp;</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; min-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; line-height: inherit; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 